    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>QMU has attained four shortlisted entries in the Converge Challenge 2018, the leading company creation competition and entrepreneurship development programme for staff, students and recent graduates of Scottish universities.</p>
<p><span>Following record-breaking entries to this year’s Converge Challenge, the QMU shortlisted entries are four of the top 60 projects from Scottish universities. The top 60 include a range of innovative ideas covering women’s health, virtual reality, renewables and environmental sustainability, demonstrating that Scotland’s pipeline of new and innovative businesses is robust and healthier than ever before.</span></p>]]></Value>
